National Safety Month: Safe Return of our Patients & Crews







	In honor of National Safety Month, our teammates have shared what it means to be safe. From our mechanics to our pilots and crews to our communication specialists at AirCom, everyone plays a role in the Safe Return of our patients and crews ... it's just in our DNA. 


